name: Teufelberger 11mm KMIII Nylon Static Rope
description: Static ropes are a good choice for rescue and descending activities. They are designed to provide high strength with low stretch and good abrasion resistance. This rope has a polyester mantle cover over a continuous filament, low twist nylon kern. This creates a rope with a low elongation factor and high tensile strength. The polyester sheath has a better resistance to chemicals such as acids.National Fire Protection Association certified.Weighs 86.3g/m.Breaking strength is 3628kg.Spool size of 183m.Sold by the metre.
